Class Agency

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.auth.Agency

java.io.Serializable
public class Agency
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The Agency class identifies an agency within the Web Curator Tool. An Agency contains a set of Users that logically belong to the agency.
